In this article, Jill expresses warm wishes to the Orthodox Christian community celebrating Easter. She rejoices in the Resurrection of Jesus Christ and the triumph of light over darkness. She also prays for those suffering from war and persecution and gives thanks to people who are helping the injured and protecting human rights. Jill calls for everyone to work towards a future with security, liberty, and justice for all. She acknowledges the contributions of Orthodox Christians in fostering understanding, advocating for the environment, and serving others. Jill looks forward to continuing this work to create a more just and compassionate world.